ugrade to latest

broken

working
fields.summary: Failed to create the parts control

comments.body:
Hello,
there are several issues here:

1. You have added different sources for installing software that are in conflict. Remove all of them, except Appcelerator's 
2. One of the addresses in the sources is wrong, remove it. 
3. Your log is quite huge. Please CLEAN the log first (Ti Studio -> Help -> Ti Studio-> Clean log) and then try to upgrade it. And share the log when done. 

Best Regards
